        "comment": "Create data for manufacturer-specific advertising data.\n.\n505 (0x01f9) is Medtronic\u0027s Bluetooth company ID.\nThe UUID changes depending on the \"forPairing\" argument. Also the first\nbyte of the actual data: 0x00 if the flag is set, 0x80 otherwise.\n.",
        "style": "LINE"
      },
